<p class="text-muted" style="max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">Clean Arcade is built on a simple idea: games should be fun, not frustrating. No ads, no sign-ups, no dark patterns.</p>

<div class="features-grid">
  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Zero Ads</h3>
    <p>No banner ads, no interstitials, no video ads before you play. The game loads and you play.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>No Tracking</h3>
    <p>No analytics, no cookies, no fingerprinting. We don't know who you are and we don't want to.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Local Saves</h3>
    <p>Your progress, high scores, and favorites are saved locally in your browser. They never leave your device.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>200 Games</h3>
    <p>Puzzle, arcade, card, board, word, strategy, sports, racing, and more. All playable in your browser.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Multiplayer</h3>
    <p>Select games support peer-to-peer multiplayer via WebRTC. Share a room code and play together.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Dark Mode</h3>
    <p>Respects your system preference or toggle manually. Easy on the eyes for late-night sessions.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Mobile Friendly</h3>
    <p>Most games work on phones and tablets. Games that need a keyboard are clearly marked.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Fast Search</h3>
    <p>Find any game instantly with search. Filter by category, difficulty, or type a name.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-card">
    <h3>Translated</h3>
    <p>Available in 30+ languages so everyone can play.</p>
  </div>
</div>
